Golf Shop
Pro shop is open from 6:30am - 6:00pm
Riding carts must be returned no later than 7:00 pm daily
We have new & used balls, tees, hats, visors, gloves and towels for sale.
We also offer chips, candy bars, soft drinks and beer.
We sell golf club grips and will regrip them for you for only $2.00 ea/club
